br></li><li> Abilities, from an aerial attack to putting the whole arena on fire - there are 14 unique of them!<br></li><li> Customization parts to change the stats and appearance of your Contrablade.<br></li><li> Incremental upgrades such as recovery, magnet, and ability cooldown and more!<br></li><li> Assign Contrablades to mine to get gems, even while the game is closed!</li></ul>",
